            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into small bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes </strong>and <strong>crushed</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> to the dish and give everything a stir</p>",
      "order": 4,
