    {
      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle in your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, add your <strong>sun-dried tomatoes </strong>and 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[400ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Tip: Nestle the potatoes into the stock as much as you can!</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
