    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and the potatoes are tender – this is your <strong>one-pot creamy sun-dried tomato & chicken stew</strong></p>",
