    {
      "instruction": "<p>To serve, remove the dish from the oven and stir your <strong>crème fraîche </strong>through the <strong>one-pot creamy sun-dried tomato & chicken stew</strong></p><p>Roughly tear your <strong>basil leaves</strong> over the top</p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and sprinkle over your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
